on of software systems will in particular profit from the individual\ncases presented.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2019 17:07:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 18 Jan 2020 19:05:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-22"}
