ergy, which implies existence of similar\npattern-forming instabilities in many other contexts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Jun 2019 20:05:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 3 Nov 2019 03:57:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-05"}
