s, the traditional choice between two spin measurement\nsettings is replaced by a choice between different times of evolution at each\nsite.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 12 Jun 2019 02:34:13 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 13 Jun 2019 05:32:16 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 22 Apr 2020 04:49:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-12"}
